metadata.name: Cybergang Vol.01
metadata.description:
a collaborative project of several artists who have different art styles and backgrounds by building a cyberpunk-themed character.
Synopsis: In the year 2099, there was a great disaster that did not make sense to humans, there was a dimensional cleavage from another world that was connected to the earth.
An unidentified creature appeared that has never been known to humans and eradicated millions of humans at that time
The surviving humans, united forces to overcome the disaster
They formed an alliance from all countries to create artificial humans with the latest technology to keep humans from extinction
